high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up a knife from the counter
Move to the sink to the left of you
Clean the knife in the sink
Move to the right side of the sink
Put the knife on the counter in front of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned knife on the counter in front of the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is sitting on the counter.
Move over to the leftmost sink basin.
Place the knife in the sink and wash it before picking it back up.
Move over to the rightmost sink basin.
Place the knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the sink.

high_descs: Go left and face the spoon on the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick the knife up that is to the right of the spoon on the counter.
Go left to face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the knife up from the sink.
Move a bit to the right of the sink.
Put the knife down on the thin piece of counter in front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife on the counter.
